response.original_title: Grand Tower: UFOs and Other High Strangeness
response.overview: 1973 was the year of high strangeness, marked by unusual phenomena, including multiple UFO sightings, bizarre creature encounters, and extraordinary paranormal activity. This investigative documentary includes eyewitness accounts that have led some to believe that an interdimensional portal may be the cause of mysterious events that have plagued a Midwestern community along the Mississippi River. Join UFO researcher Michael Huntington as he investigates encounters with high strangeness in Grand Tower, Illinois.
response.tagline: Researcher Michael Huntington investigates eyewitness reports of UFOS, bizarre creatures, and paranormal activity in Grand Tower, Illinois.
response.title: Grand Tower: UFOs and Other High Strangeness
